                                                                <customfield id="customfield_12310192" key="com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.customfieldtypes:textarea">
                        <customfieldname>Release Note</customfieldname>
                        <customfieldvalues>
                            <customfieldvalue>The patch introduces a new command line parameter for pig: -useHCatalog which imports the appropriate jars for pig use with HCatalog. This reduces the burden of finding all the relevant jars for using HCatalog with pig. If the user has setup the home directories for hive/hcatalog those would be used else defaults (/usr/lib/hive...) are assumed.</customfieldvalue>

